A New Age interpretation of this transition is that this date marks the start of time in which Earth and its inhabitants may undergo a positive spiritual transformation, that 2012 may mark the beginning of a new era. Others suggest the 2012 date marks the end of the world. Kaos Krew Records in association with Iliuchina, present their 17th digital release of 2012: Iliuchina - Apocalypse Now EP. Stay tuned for this digital release available from digital music stores on 21 December 2012. Distributed By Symphonic Distribution - www.symphonicdistribution.com
